title: Blue Coat Security Gateway: Hardware Temperature Sensors
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/bluecoat
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
  Checks by SNMP the temperature sensors of Blue Coat Security Gateways.

  Returns {OK} if an ok status is reported by SNMP and {CRIT} on any
  other status.

item:
 The sensor description as returned by SNMP

discovery:
 One service is created for each temperature sensor.
